data.description: Must see this beauty located in the sought after community of Bedford Estate.  This open floorplan comes with 6 Bedrooms and 4 Bathrooms. Bedroom on the main with full bath. Living room/Dining Room large combo. Kitchen features an oversized granite island to accommodate plenty of bar seating. Gas stove and double ovens. Keeping room for entertaining and den with fireplace and open floor plan. Spacious Walk in pantry and mudroom. Primary bedroom is huge with a sitting area and comes with a fireplace for warm cozy nights. Primary bathroom has double vanity, sep tub and shower and a supersized walk in closet. This home also showcases an additional (approximate) 1419 square feet of unfinished full basement which can be designed with an office, theater room, gym, bedroom.
